The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, reading, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, italian
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the italian##1
3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Movie-Genre      | disaster     | adventure | thriller      |
| Hobby         | reading  | writing       | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    | italian     |

